ham and split pea sop

1 bag dried split peas (flat)
rince them
drain

sautee fine chopped onion
2tbs butter
little salter

add minced garlic
add 7 cups water

add 2-3 ham steaks
3 strips of of amerival bacon
2 bay leaves
2 sprigs tymes

add peas (until tender not splitting/breaking)
simmer ~45 minutes

remove the ham steaks
shred ham with fork

add diced carrot and celery 
further simmer for ~30 minutes
discard bacon
readd ham back

top mith garlic cruitons
and mint
